title: To Livestream or not to Livestream?
description:
I have been thinking of doing a live chat in order to get to know my subscribers, here are my thoughts on the subject. If you think this would be something you'd like, pls let me now in the comments. I also go over how to properly pronounce my name...

twitter: @theother_95

Email me: theotherninetyfive@gmail.com
